      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To clarify the authority of the President to declare certain national emergencies under the National Emergencies Act, certain major disasters or emergencies under the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act, or public health emergencies under the Public Health Service Act on the premise of climate change, and for other purposes.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
